[{"conversations": [{"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "ん……？　おいユーディル。城の外で、誰か揉めてるみたいだぞ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "ランザーヴ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120009_story/VO_CHR_120009_STORY_0037.wav"], "content": "騎士待ってくれ！　イルファン！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120009_01.png", "speakerName": "騎士", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "騎士頼むから、もうしばらく我が騎士団に留まってくれ！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120009_01.png", "speakerName": "騎士", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0025.wav"], "content": "最初に言っただろ、騎士団長。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "オレが望む額の報酬を出せないなら、すぐにでも辞めさせてもらうってな。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120009_story/VO_CHR_120009_STORY_0038.wav"], "content": "う……それは、そうだが……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120009_01.png", "speakerName": "騎士", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "しかし、お前がいなくなっては、我が騎士団は立ち行かぬ……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120009_01.png", "speakerName": "騎士", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "なら金を作るんだな。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "金さえもらえりゃ、どんな仕事も完璧に果たしてやるよ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0001.wav"], "content": "なぁ！　この城にユーディル王子はいるか？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "ユーディルは、おれだけど。きみ、さっきの騎士はいいのか？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "いいんだよ、あんな貧乏人のことは。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "そんなことより……オレはイルファン。傭兵だ。オレを雇う気はねーか？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "傭兵か……確かに、戦える人手は欲しいけど、でも――", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "ならちょうどいい！　自分で言うのもなんだが、オレは使えるぜ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "金さえもらえりゃ、どんな大部隊だって、ひとりで足止めしてみせる。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "あいつの言ってることは、嘘じゃねえ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "ランザーヴ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "傭兵のイルファンと言やぁ、凄腕で有名だ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "ランザーヴ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0016.wav"], "content": "そうなのか……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "きみが仲間になってくれるなら、おれは助かるけど、でも……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0001.wav"], "content": "じゃあ雇ってくれるんだな！　よし！なら早速、報酬の相談に入ろう。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "いや、聞いてくれ。報酬のことなんだけど……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "あんた、アルベリアの王子様なんだろ？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "そんな王子様の騎士団なら、そりゃあもう金持ちなんだろうな。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0019.wav"], "content": "オレを雇ったのは正しい選択だぜ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "金さえもらえれば、オレはあんたに絶対の忠誠を誓う。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0071.wav"], "content": "報酬次第で、どんな仕事もこなす。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "金持ちなあんたの配下としちゃあ、オレは最高の――", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "いや、悪いんだけど……おれたち、懐には余裕がないんだ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0007.wav"], "content": "……え？　は？　なに言ってんだよ。あんた王子様だろ!?", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "まあ、そうだけど……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "兄上や姉上と違って、自分の領地もないし、そんなに裕福なわけでもないし……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0006.wav"], "content": "な……な……なんだそりゃ！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0025.wav"], "content": "あーそうかよ！　ならやめだ！この話はなし！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "オレは元の雇い主のところへ……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0038.wav"], "content": "……って、くそ！さっき辞めてきちまったんだった！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "な、なんだかすまないな……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……てことは、きみは仲間になってくれないのか？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0062.wav"], "content": "それは……いや、待てよ？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "今は文なしとは言え、王子だしな……いつか一国の主になる可能性もあるか。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0028.wav"], "content": "……わかった。仲間になろう。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "普段はこんなこと絶対しねーが、出世払いってことにしといてやる。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "いいのか？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "ああ。元の雇い主のところに戻っても、あいつらたいして金ねーしな……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "ただし、覚えておけよ。オレは、ただ働きは絶対にしねー。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0031.wav"], "content": "報酬は、払えるだけでも払ってもらう。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0019.wav"], "content": "オレがどれだけ働くかは、その額次第だからな。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110037011, "title": "守銭奴傭兵"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "おいユーディル。ここから先の平地、危険だぞ。待ち伏せには絶好の場所だ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "ランザーヴ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "確かにな……。でも行軍するのに、あの平地を避けて通るわけには――", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "……敵が待ち伏せしてるとすれば、平地の向こう。あの森の影だな。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "え……イルファン。敵の位置がわかるのか!?", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "こういう状況なら、今まで何度も切り抜けてきた。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "見りゃだいたいの位置はわかる。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "これ以上詳しいことが知りたいなら、斥候に出て、実際に見てくる必要があるがな。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "そうか……なら、頼めないか？きみが一番適任だと思う。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0024.wav"], "content": "断る。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "えっ？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "斥候は命懸けの仕事だ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPa