peakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0037.wav"], "content": "貴様……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "エルフィリス", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "まあまあ、エルフィリス。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "ちゃんと報酬を支払えてないおれに、非があるんだから。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "そうだ、こうしよう。斥候には、おれが行ってくる。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0002.wav"], "content": "なっ……なに馬鹿言ってんだユーディル王子！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0038.wav"], "content": "雇い主に死なれちゃ、オレが困る！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_1031.wav"], "content": "そうです！ユーディルはもう少し、人の上に立つ自覚を持つべきかと！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "エルフィリス", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0007.wav"], "content": "そんな、ふたりして怒らなくても……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0025.wav"], "content": "まったく……仕方ありません。斥候には私が行きます。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "エルフィリス", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "だから殿下は、ここでお待ちを。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "エルフィリス", 