 "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "一族を離れて暮らしてみたり、今着ているこの服も、王都で流行ってる最先端のものだしな。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "だがオレがいくら変わったところで、一族は古いしきたりに縛られたままだ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "族長の長男として、放ってはおけない。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "そうなのか……それは、心配だな。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "なんとか、一族が安全に暮らせる方法はないんだろうか……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "……考えが、ないわけじゃない。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "オレは、街を作ればいいと思ってる。一族が管理する、一族の街だ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "それなら、一族のみんなも、街で暮らすことに納得してくれるはずだ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "ただ、それには莫大な資金が……っと。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "……え。もしかしてきみが、いつもお金にこだわってるのって……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "口が滑った。今の話は、なしだ。忘れろ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "……そうか。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0027.wav"], "content": "わかった。きみが話したくないなら、これ以上聞くのはやめておこう。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "だが……ひとつだけ言わせてくれ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0032.wav"], "content": "一族のために戦うきみのこと……、おれは、立派だと思うよ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0074.wav"], "content": "う、うるせーな！忘れろって言ってるだろ！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110037013, "title": "しきたりと夢"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0026.wav"], "content": "はぁ……はぁ……。なんとか、敵は振り切ったか……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "ランザーヴ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "ああ……。だが、安心はできないぞ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "エルフィリス", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0038.wav"], "content": "敵の位置がわからないままでは、逃げ続けても、いつか追い詰められる。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "エルフィリス", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……ユーディル。ここは斥候をたて、敵の布陣を探るべきかと。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "エルフィリス", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "私が行きますので――", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "エルフィリス", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "……いや、斥候なら――イルファン、きみに頼めないだろうか？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "……イルファンに？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "エルフィリス", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "行ってもらえるなら助かりますが、どうせ断られるに決まっているような……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "エルフィリス", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "エルフィリスの言う通りだ。オレは、金にならない仕事はしない。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "斥候を頼みたいのなら他の誰かに――", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "ああ。確かに今のおれは、きみにたいした金を支払うことはできない。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "けれど……もしおれが、いずれ自分の国を持ったなら、その時は……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0032.wav"], "content": "おれの領地の一部を、イルファン、きみに与えよう。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "領地……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "エルフィリス", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "『金』ではなく『領地』ですか……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "エルフィリス", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "そう。領地だ。きみが自由に使っていい、きみの領地。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……どうかな？　イルファン。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "……まだ持ってさえいない領地の話をされてもな。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "ああ。確かにそうだな。だから、これは信用の問題だ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "おれが本当に、自分の国を持てるようになると、きみが信じられるか、否か、だ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "…………。……了解した。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0072.wav"], "content": "任せとけ。斥候くらい、さっさと済ませてきてやるよ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "なっ……！本当か、イルファン。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "エルフィリス", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "まあ、前にも言った通り、本来なら出世払いなんざお断りだがな。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "お前の約束なら、信じてみてもいい。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0060.wav"], "content": "……ユーディル。これは、いったいどういうことですか？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "エルフィリス", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0032.wav"], "content": "お金よりも大切な報酬を、約束しただけだよ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "……戻ったぞ。早速、報告をしてもいいか？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "もう戻ってきたのか？ずいぶんと早いな……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "エルフィリス", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "納得できる報酬を提示されれば、依頼主が納得できる結果を出す。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0071.wav"], "content": "それがオレの信条だ。心配すんな。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "敵の数は、オレたちの4倍。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "すでにこっちを包囲しつつあるが、まだ布陣は完璧じゃない。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "南側の包囲網は、まだ手薄だ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "オレたち全員でかかれば、楽に突破できると思うぜ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0025.wav"], "content": "はっ、ようやく本気を見せやがったか。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "ランザーヴ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "やっぱり、イルファンに頼んで正解だったな。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "だが、ユーディル。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "ランザーヴ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "いくら敵の情報がわかったとはいえ、包囲網を抜けるまでは気を抜くなよ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "ランザーヴ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "いや、ユーディル王子。気を抜いててくれて構わないぜ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "あんたのことは、オレが必ず守る。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "それだけの報酬を、もう約束してもらったんだからな。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0001.wav"], "content": "――さぁ、行くぞ！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110037014, "title": "お金よりも大切な"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "ユーディル王子。確認しておきたいことがある。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0043.wav"], "content": "ん……？　どうした、イルファン。いつになく真剣だな。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "ああ、大切な話だからな。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "おまえは自分の国を持ったら、オレに領地を与えると言ったな。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……あの言葉に、嘘はないか？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "ああ、そのことか。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0032.wav"], "content": "もちろん嘘はないよ。約束を違えるようなことはしない。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "約束を果たすまでには、まだ時間がかかるかもしれないけど――", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "きみに領地を与えるためにも、おれは全力を尽くすよ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0021.wav"], "content": "そうか。ならいいんだ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0025.wav"], "content": "にしても、全力を尽くす……か。やっぱり変わってるな、あんたは。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0007.wav"], "content": "ん？おれ、なにかおかしなこと言ったか？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "ああ。オレは本来、出世払いを信じない。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "そういう依頼主は、たいてい――", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "「出世したら金を払うんだから、出世に協力するのも仕事のうちだ」と、ただ働きを強いてくるからだ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "だが、あんたは、全力を尽くすと言った。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "オレにやらせるんじゃなく、自分の力で、約束を果たすんだと。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "きみがおれに力を貸してくれる分、おれがきみのために力を尽くすのは、当然のことだろ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "いいや。少なくとも今までの依頼主は、そうじゃなかったぜ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "あんたみたいな依頼主は初めてだ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "だからこそ、オレはあんたの出世払いを信じる気になったんだよ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "……なあ。ひとつ聞いてもいいか？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "なぜきみは、夢を語らず、いつも金が欲しいと言うんだ？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "一族を救いたいと言っていたら、おれ以外にも、力を貸してくれる依頼主がいたかもしれないのに。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0062.wav"], "content": "それは……できない相談だ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "そこいらで軽々しく夢を話したら、一族のみんなに知られる危険がある。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0025.wav"], "content": "他人に助けられるより、死を選ぶような人たちだ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "たとえオレが族長の長男でも――", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "一族を救うために、命懸けで金を集めたと知ったら、みんなは決してそれを受け入れない。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "集落を飛び出した放蕩息子が、運よく大金を手に入れたから、街を買った。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "……それでいいんだ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "だってオレが守りたいのは、一族のみんなの命だけじゃなく――", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "決して他人の手を借りない、バカみてーに古臭いが、なにより尊い……一族の誇りだからな。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "イルファン……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "だから、ユーディル王子。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0031.wav"], "content": "オレも一族の誇りを受け継ぐ者として、ここに改めて誓おう。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "オレは、あんたが願いを叶えられるように全力で協力する。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "誇り高き一族を治める族長の長男が、あんたに土地を譲ってもらうのを、ただ待ってるわけにはいかないからな。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "こんな言い方をするのは初めてだが……同じ志のため、共に戦わせてくれ。ユーディル王子。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "断る理由はないよ。頼りにしているぞ、イルファン。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0001.wav"], "content": "ああ、任せとけ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110037_story/VO_CHR_110037_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "最高の報酬を約束してもらったんだ。最高の仕事で応えてやるさ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110037_01.png", "speakerName": "イルファン", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110037015, "title": "最高の報酬"}]